Inspiration from https://adriann.github.io/programming_problems.html

To keep it simple I used https://glot.io/ for running and compiling the code

010 Write a program that asks the user for her name and greets her with her name
020 Write function that reverses a list, preferably in place
030 Write a program that automatically converts English text to Morse code and vice versa
040 Write a function that tests whether a string is a palindrome